Product Name: Online Only - Premium Jack Rabbit Thrusting Purple - Calvista

Long Description:
Meet Maybelline New York's 1st 4-in-1 makeup for a perfected glow look. Instant Perfector Glow gives skin the benefit of four products in one.
Introducing Maybelline's Instant Age Rewind Instant Perfector 4-In-1 Glow Makeup which has an illuminating formula that primes, conceals, highlights and evens skin tone with light coverage.This do-it-all makeup has everything you need to help perfect your look in an instant!
Size:  20ml

KEY FEATURES
• Now, get glowing with luminosity in an instant!
• Illuminating 4-In-1 formula - primes, conceals, highlights & evens with light coverage
• Built-in sponge applicator for an easy, quick perfected natural glow
• Self-adjusting shades that blend seamlessly into skin
• Easy application. Just swipe, mind blow!
Directions: Turn collar of applicator in direction of arrows until product is visible on sponge. This may require a number of turns the first time. Apply directly to face. Blend into skin tone.
